HEADWORD: Impassable
<hw>Im*pass"a*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Cf.
<er>Unpassable</er>.]</ety> <def>Incapable of being passed; not
admitting a passage; <as>as, an <ex>impassable</ex> road, mountain, or
gulf</as>.</def> <au>Milton.</au> --
<wordforms><wf>Im*pass"a*ble*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos> --
<wf>Im*pass"a*bly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
